Klopp on summer signings: We will show that we learned from this year... Of course we will bring in players, the squad will change.<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;Next season with more games we will need to have more options and that is clear.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;We have options, we can change systems. Phil, Lucas, Milner could play wing-back, possibly.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot; I said to Sturridge - it's the perfect moment to come back to training. We don't think about who we miss but who we can work with.&quot;
